article_title: 'Free Stuff' or a free America, you can't have both
article_text:
Northfield, MN (55057)

Today

Rain. Thunderstorms possible...mainly in the afternoon. High near 75F. Winds ESE at 5 to 10 mph. Chance of rain 80%..

Tonight

Cloudy with showers likely late, and possibly a thunderstorm. Low around 60F. Winds ENE at 5 to 10 mph. Chance of rain 70%.
